title: Holiday Steals Game 5, a Warriors Stinkfest, and Offseason Roulette | Group Chat
description:
Justin, Rob, and Wos discuss Giannis’s big game in the Bucks’ comeback road win (2:46). Then they review Memphis’s domination of the Warriors to force a Game 6 (28:37). Finally, they raise some offseason story lines with a game of Offseason Roulette (40:31).

Hosts: Justin Verrier, Rob Mahoney, Wosny Lambre
Associate Producer: Carlos Chiriboga
